  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Aristotle
Lived:         384 - -322
Nationality:   Greek
Field:         Philosophy
Known For:     Logic, ethics, biology
Contribution:  Codified logic; wrote on biology, physics, ethics, politics; tutored Alexander
Quote:         "The more you know, the more you know you don't know."

Name:          Alan Turing
Lived:         1912 - 1954
Nationality:   English
Field:         Computing
Known For:     Turing machine, codebreaking
Contribution:  Father of computer science; broke Enigma; Turing test for AI
Quote:         "We can only see a short distance ahead, but we can see plenty there that needs to be done."

Name:          Galileo Galilei
Lived:         1564 - 1642
Nationality:   Italian
Field:         Astronomy
Known For:     Heliocentrism, telescope
Contribution:  Confirmed Copernican model; law of falling bodies; faced Inquisition
Quote:         "And yet it moves."

